      <div resp="part:emfr" type="translation">
        <p n="1-4"><supplied reason="subaudible">This is</supplied> the stone of Koṟṟantai Kōṭaṉ, the servant of Viṇṇappērēṉati.</p>
      </div>
      <div type="commentary">
        <p>On the same slab, two heroes (Viṇṇapērēṉāti and Koṟṟantai Kōṭaṉ, servant of Viṇṇapērēṉāti), each with his own representation and with his own inscription. See DHARMA_INSPallava00529.</p>
      </div>
