          </bibl> (EI 39, no. 33A.II); text in <bibl>
            <ptr target="bib:Dayalan2005_01"></ptr>
          </bibl>; encoded and translated here for DHARMA (ERC n° 809994) by Emmanuel Francis (2022), based on previous edition(s) and published visual documentation.</p>
